    "href": "viewer.html?file=CN/Apps/%E8%B6%A3%E5%91%B3App%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%94%B6%E5%BD%95.md#1-蓝牙/ble-类",
    "parent": "Flipper Zero 趣味 App 完全收录"
