    "text": "Flipper Zero Fun Apps Collection 8.4 DCF77 Clock Spoof Attribute | Details -----------|--------- **Source** | Official Catalog **Catalog** | ✅ applications/Tools/dcf77_clock_spoof **GitHub** | https://github.com/molodos/dcf77-clock-spoof.git **Author** | @Molodos **What does it do?** Forge DCF77 time signal. DCF77 is Germany's longwave time signal transmitter. European radio clocks sync to it. This tool sends forged signals to make nearby radio clocks sync to your chosen time. **Technical points:** Longwave time signal protocol RF signal modulation RFID antenna as transmitter **How to play:** Test radio clocks Study time sync protocols Learn about radio time systems ---",
