    "summary": "Every Flipper Zero task should be routed into one of these 6 categories: Device usage / menu / data management External App / FAP Firmware / System Programming JavaScript Hardware Expansion / GPIO / Dev Board File Format",
    "text": "FlipperZero AI Pack (English) 2. Classify the task before answering Every Flipper Zero task should be routed into one of these 6 categories: Device usage / menu / data management External App / FAP Firmware / System Programming JavaScript Hardware Expansion / GPIO / Dev Board File Formats / Data Conversion / Asset Handling Default routing rules: if it can be an external app, prefer the FAP route first if it is a lightweight script or automation task, prefer JavaScript if it involves sensors, coprocessors, serial, ESP32, or Dev Boards, route to Hardware Expansion only enter Firmware when system-level changes are clearly required if it involves import, export, parsing, conversion, persistence, or generated assets, switch immediately to File Formats",
