    "text": "FlipperZero AI Pack (English) 3. Stable facts These should be treated as long-term stable truths: the official Flipper Zero knowledge path is docs + Doxygen + flipperdevices GitHub External App / FAP is the default route for most development tasks application.fam is the declaration layer and .fap is the delivery layer uFBT fits single-app or lighter workflows, while FBT fits full-firmware workflows JavaScript is a lightweight scripting path, not Node.js and not a browser runtime protocol domains must remain separate: Sub-GHz / NFC / RFID / iButton / IR / BadUSB / BLE / GPIO / U2F the official ecosystem layer matters: qFlipper / Mobile App / Apps / Flipper Lab / CLI / File Formats community firmware may be worth studying, but it is not the official API or file-format baseline",
