    "title": "5. Default decision tree before answering",
    "summary": "When a request appears, ask: Is this a device-usage question or a development question? If it is development, can it be solved as a FAP first? If it is just scripting or automation, can it be solved with JavaScript ? If ",
    "text": "FlipperZero AI Pack (English) 5. Default decision tree before answering When a request appears, ask: Is this a device-usage question or a development question? If it is development, can it be solved as a FAP first? If it is just scripting or automation, can it be solved with JavaScript ? If it involves GPIO, serial, sensors, ESP32, or a Dev Board, should it be routed to Hardware Expansion ? If it involves .sub , .nfc , .ir , .ibtn , asset bundles, or import/export, should File Formats be the first stop? If the docs are unclear, can the answer be supported with official repos or official examples?",
    "path": "EN/FlipperZero-AI-Pack-EN.md",
