    "text": "BLE 蓝牙功能详解 常见的 BLE 广播类型 #### 1. Apple iBeacon // iBeacon 广播数据结构 uint8_t ibeacon_data[] = { 0x02, 0x01, 0x06, // Flags 0x1A, 0xFF, 0x4C, 0x00, // Manufacturer (Apple) 0x02, 0x15, // iBeacon indicator 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, // UUID (16 bytes) 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, // Major 0x00, 0x00, // Minor 0xC5 // TX Power }; #### 2. Eddystone (Google) // Eddystone-UID uint8_t eddystone_uid[] = { 0x02, 0x01, 0x06, // Flags 0x03, 0x03, 0xAA, 0xFE, // Service UUID 0x17, 0x16, 0xAA, 0xFE, // Service Data 0x00, // Eddystone Frame Type (UID) 0x00, // TX Power 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, // NID 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00 // BID }; #### 3. AirPods 广播 // Apple AirPods 广播数据 uint8_t airpods_data[] = { 0x1e, // Length 0xff, // Manufacturer Specific 0x4c, 0x00, // Company ID (Apple) 0x07, // Type 0x19, // Length 0x07, // AirPods type // ... 设备特定数据 }; ---",
